<p><b>Sobha Singh</b> (29 November 1901 – 22 August 1986)<sup id="cite_ref-.E0.A8.AA.E0.A9.B0.E0.A8.9C.E0.A8.BE.E0.A8.AC_.E0.A8.95.E0.A9.8B.E0.A8.B8.E0.A8.BC_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-.E0.A8.AA.E0.A9.B0.E0.A8.9C.E0.A8.BE.E0.A8.AC_.E0.A8.95.E0.A9.8B.E0.A8.B8.E0.A8.BC-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> was a well-known contemporary painter from Indian <a href="/wiki/Punjab,_India" title="Punjab, India">Punjab</a>.</p>
<p></p>
